INSERT INTO `activity` VALUES (29, '日本帝国的扩张 | TELL+历史讲座：二战与现代世界第一讲', '我们提起发生在漫长过去的那些事的原因，在于未来。历史是往复循环中的生生不息，令我们在现实中更加理性的思考和行动，人类社会因而在螺旋中每一次都得以向前缓慢移动，而非停留在自己的影子里。TELL+历史的意义也就在于此。', 'TELL+历史讲座;二战', 'http://localhost:8080/upload/background/2019-02-26829132.JPG', '<p><img src=\"/upload/activity/2019-02-26/2019-02-26941218.JPG\" style=\"width: 647px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 我们提起发生在漫长过去的那些事的原因，在于未来。历史是往复循环中的生生不息，令我们在现实中更加理性的思考和行动，人类社会因而在螺旋中每一次都得以向前缓慢移动，而非停留在自己的影子里。TELL+历史的意义也就在于此。<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 现代世界的形成，与第二次世界大战有着密切的关系，了解第二次世界大战的起因经过和结果，能够加深对当下世界面临的问题的认识。2019年TELL将通过七场讲座，分别讲述二战欧洲战场及太平洋战场，并重点分析战争与欧洲国家以及亚洲国家形成之间的关系。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/upload/activity/2019-02-26/2019-02-2697579.JPG\" style=\"width: 647px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;众所周知，第二次世界大战是今日世界格局之形成的基础。但在德国历史学家的眼中，没有所谓的WW1和WW2，只有从1914年开始，到1945年结束的“第二次三十年战争”。无论怎么定义世界大战，对于那场人类史上的巨大浩劫，相信对于很多人而言，却是熟悉却又陌生的。我们或许会满足于某些兵器的性能，某位空战或者陆战王牌的战绩，这些是二战的重要组成部分，但并不是二战的全部。那么，我所讲的会是怎样的故事？</span><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\"><br></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\"><img src=\"/upload/activity/2019-02-26/2019-02-26199176.JPEG\" style=\"width: 647px;\"><img src=\"/upload/activity/2019-02-26/2019-02-26761934.JPG\" style=\"width: 646.672px; height: 323.336px;\"><br></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 这一讲，我们会从二战的太平洋战场开始。只不过，我们所要反思的是，这一片废墟的背后的原因。一个崛起于19世纪最后几年，用十几年的时间开始挤进当时发达国家的“圈子”，然后又以火箭般的速度陨落，这就是我们的近邻—日本。我们需要去了解这个国家的成长和战略，毕竟它曾带给我们巨大的痛苦和灾难。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">国家战略，决定的是可能是数亿人的生死。而讲述其中常识和逻辑，将会构成解说历史的巨大意义。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(200, 12, 18); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">二战，并不久远的回忆</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(200, 12, 18); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">第一卷：日本帝国的扩张</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(200, 12, 18); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(200, 12, 18); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">敬请期待！</span></p>', 175, 0, 0, 1, 0, '2019-04-02 13:11:48', '2019-02-26 18:30:09', 1, 5, 15);
INSERT INTO `activity` VALUES (30, '“她世界她力量”2019中国女性领导力高峰论坛正式开启', '“她世界她力量”2019中国女性领导力高峰论坛，是由智联招聘首创发起，以提升中国职场女性幸福感为目标，从不同角度出发为职场女性发声，帮助职场女性打破社会认知偏见和自我认知局限的公益活动。每年3月，国内外数千万职场女性和全国近百家权威媒体将莅临活动现场共同探讨职场女性的现状与发展。', '女性领导力;高峰论坛', 'http://localhost:8080/upload/background/2019-02-26433171.JPG', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(30, 28, 17); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">活动介绍&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(30, 28, 17); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p pingfang=\"\" helvetica=\"\" microsoft=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 11px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(30, 28, 17); font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“她世界她力量”2019中国女性领导力高峰论坛，是由智联招聘首创发起，以提升中国职场女性幸福感为目标，从不同角度出发为职场女性发声，帮助职场女性打破社会认知偏见和自我认知局限的公益活动。每年3月，国内外数千万职场女性和全国近百家权威媒体将莅临活动现场共同探讨职场女性的现状与发展。</span><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p pingfang=\"\" helvetica=\"\" microsoft=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" widows:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 11px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(30, 28, 17); letter-spacing: 1px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;迄今为止，“她世界她力量”中国女性领导力高峰论坛已成功举办三届，邀请了<span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">联合国妇女署亲善大使佟大为、联合国妇女署前国别项目主任Julia Broussard、前时尚集团总裁苏芒、著名导演李少红、紫牛资金创始管理合伙人张泉灵、</span><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">蜜芽创始人刘楠<span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-weight: bolder; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">、</span>米果文化副董事长马薇薇、</span><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Uber中国区前负责人柳甄</span>等来自不同领域的精英人士汇聚一堂，与现场数千位观众分享他们的职场历程和人生感悟，共同探讨当下职场女性面临的困境及未来发展之路。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(30, 28, 17); letter-spacing: 1px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2017年，智联招聘与联合国妇女署签署战略合作协议，<span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">联合国妇女署作为智联招聘女性职场性别平等项目特别支持机构</span>，全程支持女性论坛的开展。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(30, 28, 17); letter-spacing: 1px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2018年，“她世界她力量” 中国女性领导力高峰论坛由联合国妇女署、智联招聘共同主办。<span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">奥运冠军邓亚萍，<span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-weight: bolder; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">联合国妇女署前国别项目主任Julia Broussard<span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-weight: bolder; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">，</span></span>中央戏剧学院导师刘天池，京东集团首席人力资源官兼法律总顾问隆雨，美国洛杉矶前副市长陈愉，快看漫画创始人&amp;CEO陈安妮，空中网创始人、乐博资本创始人杨宁</span>出席现场并进行主题演讲，国内外数千万职场女性和全国近百家权威媒体聚焦现场共同探讨职场女性的现状与发展。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(30, 28, 17); letter-spacing: 1px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiase