INSERT INTO `activity` VALUES (31, '“大声秀出你的声音”～南京城市朗读2019招募喜欢朗读的你！', '2019已经到来；    你是否想在新年里给自己一个机会？    你是否想锻炼自己的勇气？    你是否愿意让自己的声音给更多人听见？', '朗读;锻炼勇气', 'http://localhost:8080/upload/background/2019-02-26404461.JPG', '<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2019已经到来；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">你是否想在新年里给自己一个机会？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">你是否想锻炼自己的勇气？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">你是否愿意让自己的声音给更多人听见？</span><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">我们每周都有线上剧本朗读及各种朗读活动，每次时间严格控制在60分钟；每次朗读结束都安排有专业的老师进行点评；让你不断的进步。更重要的是，你可以认识一群对戏剧对朗读志同道合的朋友。一起享受朗读带来的快乐。</span><br></p><p><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">每个月，我们都有精彩的线下活动，话剧演出、朗读沙龙等精彩非常；群内的伙伴可以优先预定活动名额，便利赛全家 哈哈</span><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/upload/activity/2019-02-26/2019-02-26529112.JPG\" style=\"width: 636px;\"><img src=\"/upload/activity/2019-02-26/2019-02-26321350.JPG\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 636px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">我们是谁？<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">【幸福莊戏剧工作坊】是國內规模最大的职业戏剧教育組織；主要服務對象為成人和儿童；幸福莊在上海、苏州、南京、杭州四地共拥有8个演出团队，正式注册成员超过200人。幸福莊自觉肩负国人戏剧普及的责任，拥有的戏剧活动遍布上海、苏州、南京、无锡、杭州等多个城市；共有超过5000人次参加过我们的活动。<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">幸福莊拥有自己的戏剧表演课程体系，我们的成人和儿童课程与全世界戏剧最前沿的美国纽约和英国伦敦保持一致，拥有最新的创造性戏剧的体系指引，国内独一无二。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">主要舞台剧作品：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">《朱丽小姐》、《嫁给经济适用男》、《哥本哈根》、《枕头人》、《心心相印》、《小王子》、《萨勒姆的女巫》、《主角登场》、《十二磅钱的神情》、《八美千娇》、《收信快乐》、《婴儿杀戮》、《恋爱的犀牛》等，观看观众人数超过3000人。</span><br></span></p>', 250, 0, 0, 1, 0, '2019-03-31 16:16:57', '2019-02-26 18:48:54', 1, 7, 9);
INSERT INTO `activity` VALUES (32, '读书会《超级符号就是超级创意》', '在《超级符号就是超级创意》书中有说明：“宣传的力量来源于重复，这是一切政治宣传家的常识，但却往往被企业品牌营销部门所遗忘。”', '读书;创意', 'http://localhost:8080/upload/background/2019-02-26761100.JPG', '<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">曾经大家最讨厌的广告就是“恒源祥”，总是在黄金时间连播三遍“恒源祥，羊羊羊”，画面很丑，声音也不好听。之后脑白金就开始风靡神州大地，到处都是“今年过节不收礼，收礼只收脑白金”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"https://timgsa.baidu.com/timg?image&amp;quality=80&amp;size=b9999_10000&amp;sec=1550062224271&amp;di=aba663e9e1dd7fef114143ed01b50011&amp;imgtype=0&amp;src=http%3A%2F%2Fs13.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F0021rHjzzy74kH55A6wec\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; float: none; width: 636px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">后来，当我们了解了一些品牌传播的策略，看过史玉柱的自传，尽管大家仍然讨厌这两个广告，但不得不承认它们的传播影响力还是很强的。针对这一现象，在《超级符号就是超级创意》书中有说明：“宣传的力量来源于重复，这是一切政治宣传家的常识，但却往往被企业品牌营销部门所遗忘。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"https://timgsa.baidu.com/timg?image&amp;quality=80&amp;size=b9999_10000&amp;sec=1550062713135&amp;di=899d13e305edd95188ef4cf088e2ab59&amp;imgtype=jpg&amp;src=http%3A%2F%2Fimg3.imgtn.bdimg.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3098878348%2C2246599013%26fm%3D214%26gp%3D0.jpg\" width=\"259\" height=\"361\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; width: 318px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important; word-break: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这本书的作者是<span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-weight: 700; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important;\">华杉与华楠</span>，他们是华与华营销咨询公司的联合创始人，也许你对这个名字还不熟悉，但你一定听过或看过他们创造的广告：</span></p><blockquote style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; padding-top: 20px; padding-bottom: 20px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; border-left-width: 6px; border-left-color: rgb(180, 180, 180); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); line-height: 30px; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important; word-break: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important; word-break: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-weight: 700; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important;\">“小葵花妈妈开课了”</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important; word-break: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-weight: 700; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important;\">“晒足180天，厨邦酱油美味鲜”</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important; word-break: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-weight: 700; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important;\">“I&nbsp; ❤️ 莜”，西贝莜面村</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important; word-break: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-weight: 700; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important;\">“田七——”（牙膏广告）</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important; word-break: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-weight: 700; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important;\">“三精的钙，蓝瓶的钙”</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important; word-break: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-weight: 700; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important;\">“一个北京城，四个孔雀城”</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important; word-break: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-weight: 700; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important;\">“送长辈、黄金酒”</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important; word-break: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-weight: 700; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important;\">“我爱北京天安门正南50公里”...</span></p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-bottom: 25px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; user-select: text !important; word-break: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">他们服务的客户有奇虎360、云南白药、晨光文具、葵花制药、海底捞等等，可以说，走到中国任何一个角落，超市、药店、书店、电视、互联网，你都可以随处看到华与华的作品。</span><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; background-color: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">此书是多年来第一次公开分享他们公司的核心方法论，被众多营销大咖奉为圭臬。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">​<img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/3920099-88f6302b220bd918.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 636px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">三精蓝瓶</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">相对于之前读过的《定位》,《超级符号就是超级创意》中所讲的案例接近生活，与消费者息息相关，非常接地气。作者总结的“华与华方法”通俗易懂，一招制敌，可以说是品牌建立及传播的武林秘籍，无论是你是设计师、企业老板、广告人、营销人看完都会有所启发……</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">良言录本期读书会邀请到拥有十年广告行业从业经验，曾就职大唐灵狮，银都奥美等一线广告公司，现任石唯玉文化产业有限公司品牌总监的施庆义先生，从品牌传播与亲身案例经验带我们走入广告人的世界。欢迎各界行业优秀人士报名参加，共同探讨交流！</span></p>', 70, 0, 0, 1, 0, '2019-04-01 18:43:37', '2019-02-26 18:55:02', 1, 7, 15);
