24px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-family: tahoma, arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, u5b8bu4f53, sans-serif; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-family: tahoma, arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, u5b8bu4f53, sans-serif; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">许巍，1968年生，陕西西安人。内地摇滚音乐界的重要人物。1995年许巍作词作曲的《执着》由田震演唱而广为流传。1997年4月红星生产社发行许巍首张专辑《在别处》。1998年作品被选入中国当代诗歌文选。2000年11月发行第二张专辑《那一年》 。2002年发行第三张专辑《时光·漫步》，凭借专辑获得第3届音乐风云榜zui佳摇滚专辑、zui佳摇滚歌手奖，歌曲《礼物》获得zui佳摇滚单曲、内地年度十大金曲奖 。2010年在蒙牛酸酸乳音乐风云榜十年盛典上被组委会授予“中国十年zui具影响力音乐人物”的荣誉 。2013年1月29日许巍签约歌华莱恩，“此时此刻”巡演正式启动。2014年8月，许巍与精英团队、英国旅游局，前往英国朝圣摇滚精神，并联手打造《在那摇滚的故乡》音乐旅行系列品质记录片。2015年3月，许巍为纪录片《第三极》演唱的同名主题曲发布。同年7月，为真人秀《我们15个》创作的单曲《灿烂》发布。2018年4月，为动画大电影《猫与桃花源》所创作的EP《无人知晓》发布。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(54, 96, 146); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">专辑介绍<span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-weight: bolder; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: tahoma, arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, u5b8bu4f53, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: tahoma, arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, u5b8bu4f53, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">时隔六载 如约到来 爱之少年 无尽光芒</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: tahoma, arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, u5b8bu4f53, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　许巍全新创作专辑《无尽光芒》</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: tahoma, arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, u5b8bu4f53, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: tahoma, arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, u5b8bu4f53, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　2012年12月12日，许巍上一张专辑《此时此刻》正式发行；时隔六年，最新专辑《无尽光芒》呈现在人们眼前。如果说上一张《此时此刻》专辑给人的感觉是出世恬静、自然自性的，这张时隔六载的《无尽光芒》则呈现了一种截然不同、令人惊喜的状态——优美动听的旋律里流动着无比真挚的情感，每个音符、每句歌词都浸染着对生活的热爱；专辑别有匠心的视觉融入到音乐之中，无不充满了生命和温暖的力量。</p>', 60, 0, 0, 1, 1, '2019-04-01 12:02:27', '2019-02-26 20:16:54', 1, 11, 1);
INSERT INTO `activity` VALUES (38, '迷——法国印象主义艺术家弗雷德里克·佩耶个展', '弗雷德里克在马达加斯加（法国殖民地）出生，现在在美国生活并经营着自己的画廊，认真地做一个印象派艺术家，他的作品以「神秘的活力」著称。 ', '弗雷德里克·佩耶;个人展;迷', 'http://localhost:8080/upload/background/2019-02-26660613.JPG', '<h3 style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 8.5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 1; color: rgb(11, 30, 48); font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" id=\"nav1_1\">展览内容</h3><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">弗雷德里克在马达加斯加（法国殖民地）出生，现在在美国生活并经营着自己的画廊，认真地做一个印象派艺术家，他的作品以「神秘的活力」著称。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">在艺术之都巴黎长大和工作，并没有促使他接触艺术，反而因为曾经生活的不愉快而离开了这里。直到去了那个地方..&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://cdn.huodongxing.com/file/20160806/115274E57DDF93BC179389CD47D8799B84/30843303577566812.jpg\" title=\"微信图片_20190116144846.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190116144846.jpg\" width=\"617\" height=\"616\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; height: 616px; width: 617px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">1989年，已经29岁的弗雷德里克移居到美国亚特兰大（美国东南部佐治亚州的首府）和爸爸一起生活。佩耶为了尽快适应这里的生活，接受了大伯的邀请去他的画廊工作。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">弗雷德里克的大伯运营的画廊专门研究18世纪、19世纪和20世纪的古董画。几年间，大伯的工作和画廊带给弗雷德里克不可估量的艺术认知和影响，让他开始尝试用画刷画画。大伯发现，弗雷德里克对绘画创作充满天分和想法，他的第一幅画几天就被人买走了，所以一直鼓励他大胆地去尝试更多。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">弗雷德里克就这样走上了「自学成才」的道路。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">创作风格：调色刀&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://cdn.huodongxing.com/file/20160806/115274E57DDF93BC179389CD47D8799B84/30983303578376842.jpg\" title=\"微信图片_20190116144853.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190116144853.jpg\" width=\"620\" height=\"629\" style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; height: 629px; width: 620px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; line-height: 21px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family: &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &q