kit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"https://wanzhoumo-cdn.4k1.cn/data/public/activity/2019/01/16_14/1547621819684_811446.jpg!720\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 328px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"https://wanzhoumo-cdn.4k1.cn/data/public/activity/2019/01/16_14/1547621826018_723559.jpg!720\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 328px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">印象画是他的主要风格&nbsp;<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">但绝不是他唯一的风格&nbsp;<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">抽象：&nbsp;<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">弗雷德里克从来没有接受过任何的专业训练，却总是从其他艺术家的作品身上获取灵感。他喜欢尝试新的技法和风格，以致于他的作品风格是印象派、抽象派、文艺复兴传统派与拼贴艺术之和。&nbsp;<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">抽象画&nbsp;<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"https://wanzhoumo-cdn.4k1.cn/data/public/activity/2019/01/16_14/1547621858870_530129.jpg!720\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 328px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"https://wanzhoumo-cdn.4k1.cn/data/public/activity/2019/01/16_14/1547621870061_533367.jpg!720\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 328px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></div><div class=\"zw-rich-text\" style=\"padding: 18px 15px 32px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; transform: translateZ(0px); color: rgb(96, 96, 96); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"https://wanzhoumo-cdn.4k1.cn/data/public/activity/2019/01/16_14/1547621879875_481806.jpg!720\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 328px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">双重身份&nbsp;<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">艺术家“情感密码”&nbsp;<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"https://wanzhoumo-cdn.4k1.cn/data/public/activity/2019/01/16_14/1547621912285_545904.jpg!720\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 328px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">弗雷德里克是国际“情感密码”疗愈师，自2004年以来帮助他人识别和释放负面情绪。&nbsp;<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">「“情感密码”是一种能量治疗技术，可以帮助我们识别和彻底释放负面情绪——这些情绪来自过去的负面经历。负面情绪会导致抑郁、焦虑，组织人们去爱和寻找幸福，并对身边的人产生疏远感。负面情绪是由能量构成的，就像组成身体的其他部分一样。它们会对身体组织产生影响，并可能引起严重疼痛甚至癌症。」&nbsp;<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">释放负面情绪会使身体慢慢痊愈，进而身体和情感上的问题都会消失或变得更易于控制。&nbsp;<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">由于弗雷德里克26年以来一直从事艺术工作，因此看到了艺术对人类心灵的疗愈和恢复效果。所以，他坚信颜色可以引起更多认同感，通过视觉冲击改变大脑运作的方式。&nbsp;<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"https://wanzhoumo-cdn.4k1.cn/data/public/activity/2019/01/16_14/1547621935730_414826.jpg!720\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 328px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">最佳艺术奖&nbsp;<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">英国伊斯顿艺术博览会&nbsp;<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"https://wanzhoumo-cdn.4k1.cn/data/public/activity/2019/01/16_14/1547621966220_097207.jpg!720\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 328px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></div><div><br></div></div>', 90, 0, 0, 0, 1, '2019-03-31 15:58:29', '2019-02-26 20:28:57', 1, 12, 15);
INSERT INTO `activity` VALUES (47, '将门2019年度创新峰会', '三年前，以“让技术创新真正激活商业场景，实现价值”为目标，以发掘真正的技术创新者，和连接技术型初创企业与拥有丰富商业场景的大企业为行动，将门以“让创新获得认可”为使命，应运而生。', '创业;将门;创新', 'http://localhost:8080/upload/background/2019-03-26560059.JPG', '<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 21px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">三年前，以“让技术创新真正激活商业场景，实现价值”为目标，以发掘真正的技术创新者，和连接技术型初创企业与拥有丰富商业场景的大企业为行动，将门以“让创新获得认可”为使命，应运而生。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0pt 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 21px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0pt 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 21px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">如今，将门已成长为行业领先大企业的开放式创新服务商，为其提供数字化创新战略咨询及落地验证服务。同时，将门在三年中已帮助超过800家的中国创新创业企业，连接和获取着早期重要企业标杆客户，推动创新成长。去年三月举办的首届将门年度创新峰会，将门携手科技圈的技术大咖们，集结来自交通、医疗、零售、家庭等领域的数十家行业引领大企业以及优秀的创业企业们，共同探讨AI落地产业发展的现在及未来，成为了创新创业圈里大小企业共话创新、最具影响力的开年标志性活动，打造了技术赋能产业转型升级发展的风向标。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0pt 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 21px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0pt 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 21px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2019年3月30日，<span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">将门</span>将在北京798艺术区举办<span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">第二届将门年度创新峰会</span>，本次大会以<span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: bolder; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“科技实用主义”</span>为主题，聚焦技术与产业的深度融合，邀请科技圈技术领袖、行业领先企业以及技术创新企业齐聚一堂，共同探讨最新场景创新趋势，以及技术落地产业发展的现在及未来。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0pt 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 21px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0pt 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 21px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">届时，微软、平安、新城、万达、MARS、沃尔玛、博世、三一、泰雷兹等数十家世界五百强及中国行业领先企业代表将到场，共话前沿科技、创新技术与商业落地。超过500位创新企业创始人和创新技术人、产业代表参会。演员&amp;小鱼在家代言人姚晨也会来到现场与我们一起探索“科技实用主义”的魅力。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0pt 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 21px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0pt 0in; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 0in; line-height: 21px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">同时，在峰会现场还会有来自交通、制造、零售、地产等多行业的优秀创业企业的互动展区来展示其最新潮产品和最具创意的理念。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">​<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-fa