hing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(102, 43, 149); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">关于艺术家</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">郭城，1988年出生，先后获得上海同济大学工业设计工学学士与英国皇家艺术学院产品设计文学硕士，2013年至今兼职任教于上海同济大学。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">刘月，1981年出生，2005年毕业于上海大学美术学院油画系, 目前生活和工作于上海。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">毛晨雨，1976年出生，电影作者，艺术家，稻电影和麋鹿大学项目主持。2016年开始共组“谷神变”团队，策划系列展览项目。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">铁木尔·斯琴，1984年出生，德国和中国蒙古混血，毕业于美国亚利桑那州立大学，现居纽约。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">王凝慧，1983年出生，先后获得多伦多大学计算机科学和国际关系学士学位，以及加州艺术学院艺术学士学位和纽约大学艺术硕士学位，现任上海纽约大学的客座助理教授。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://www.huodongxing.com/file/20180706/1114F8F973F1BD7C7917020D86A6F0DC13/30463360864908363.jpeg\" title=\"展览“追踪末日松茸”读本.gif\" alt=\"展览“追踪末日松茸”读本.gif\" width=\"529\" height=\"394\" style=\"-webkit-font-sm