INSERT INTO `activity` VALUES (66, 'ceshi', 'ceshi', 'ceshi', 'http://localhost:8080/upload/background/2019-04-02950408.JPG', '<p style=\"box-sizing: content-box;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/upload/activity/2019-02-26/2019-02-26941218.JPG\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; border-style: none; width: 647px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: content-box;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 我们提起发生在漫长过去的那些事的原因，在于未来。历史是往复循环中的生生不息，令我们在现实中更加理性的思考和行动，人类社会因而在螺旋中每一次都得以向前缓慢移动，而非停留在自己的影子里。TELL+历史的意义也就在于此。<br style=\"box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 现代世界的形成，与第二次世界大战有着密切的关系，了解第二次世界大战的起因经过和结果，能够加深对当下世界面临的问题的认识。2019年TELL将通过七场讲座，分别讲述二战欧洲战场及太平洋战场，并重点分析战争与欧洲国家以及亚洲国家形成之间的关系。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: content-box;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/upload/activity/2019-02-26/2019-02-2697579.JPG\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; border-style: none; width: 647px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: content-box; letter-spacing: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;众所周知，第二次世界大战是今日世界格局之形成的基础。但在德国历史学家的眼中，没有所谓的WW1和WW2，只有从1914年开始，到1945年结束的“第二次三十年战争”。无论怎么定义世界大战，对于那场人类史上的巨大浩劫，相信对于很多人而言，却是熟悉却又陌生的。我们或许会满足于某些兵器的性能，某位空战或者陆战王牌的战绩，这些是二战的重要组成部分，但并不是二战的全部。那么，我所讲的会是怎样的故事？</span><br style=\"box-sizing: content-box;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: content-box; letter-spacing: normal;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: content-box;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: content-box; letter-spacing: normal;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/upload/activity/2019-02-26/2019-02-26199176.JPEG\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; border-style: none; width: 647px;\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/upload/activity/2019-02-26/2019-02-26761934.JPG\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; border-style: none; width: 646.672px; height: 323.336px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: content-box;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 这一讲，我们会从二战的太平洋战场开始。只不过，我们所要反思的是，这一片废墟的背后的原因。一个崛起于19世纪最后几年，用十几年的时间开始挤进当时发达国家的“圈子”，然后又以火箭般的速度陨落，这就是我们的近邻—日本。我们需要去了解这个国家的成长和战略，毕竟它曾带给我们巨大的痛苦和灾难。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: content-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 